name: Autex Installation
Has the correct amount of pins been installed?
Do all the pins line up?
Have the panels been installed with a 25mm negative?
Are all the negatives consistent?
Does the panels line up throughout the bay?
Do all panels have domes on the end of all the pins?
Do the panels line up with the panel next to them?
Has the panel been cut using a sharp blade and have a clean finish?
Are all of the edges of the panels securely fixed to the underside of the ceiling?
Has the panel been cleaned?
Suspended 2-way Ceiling
Hanger Installation (before grid install)
Set out as per the plans provided (or specified)?
Solid fixing of hangers to above structure?
Hangers are spaced at 1200mm max. on to main T's?
Hangers are set more than 50mm min. from services?
Appropriate (specified ) fixings have been used?
2-way Grid System Installation
Does the grid or trim have visual dents, bends or scratches?
Is the trim set at the correct height?
Appropriate fixings have been used to fix trim to walls?
Fixings of trim to walls set at correct centres?
Clean joins on trim butts and mitres?
Trim is set level?
Grid is set level?
Main T's and nogs have been set square?
Hanger to Main T's fixed correctly? i.e. 3 turns minimum for wire, 2 waiver screws for solid unless otherwise specified.
Specified fixings of grid to trim set at correct centres? i.e. pop rivets, Berg clips etc.
Seismic gap (if any) installed with the specified size and support?
Tile Installation
Visual inspection of tiles for marks and scratches performed before and after install?
Tiles positioned correctly within the grid system?
Material has not been stored on top of installed ceiling tiles?
Correct ceiling tile type has been installed?
